makeStateChanges

public void makeStateChanges(DialogContext dc,
                             int stage)
Checks each field to make sure the state of it needs to be changed or not usually based on Conditionals. IMPORTANT: If any changes are made in this class, make sure that they are also reflected in QuerySelectDialog and QueryBuilderDialog classes which extend this class but they overwrite this method and doesn't make a call to this method.
